'''Tinml''' nɣ d '''Aɣrbaz''' iga tasntut n usslmd nna ɣ ttlmadn inlmadn timsirin d kigan n tussniwin da gis ttili tɣri s tugt n tmsirin igan tamnzut d tanammast d tasmuttgt tasinant, ism nns tiɣri tamnzut n bzziz ɣ kigan n tmizar. Da bḍḍun tinmal s tinmal n tnbaḍt d tinmal uslign d tinmal ignsann.

Ɣ tugt n tmizar, ur iga wadduy s tinml s bzziz, maca iga "usslmd n iḥnjirn" mkan. lla kra tdrsa g ibabatn nna istin ad sslmdn tarwa nnsn ɣ tgmmi . Issnti usslmd n bzziz zɣ usggas wis sḍis nɣ wis sa ɣ wawtay n warraw.

Issnti usslmd n bzziz s wadaf s tinml ɣ usggas wis sḍis. Ɣ tmsirt ad ittktasab uḥnjir tirsal n tiɣri d tirra d usiḍn. Tga tmsirt bahra imqqurn acku da ttaws i unlmad d tbnnu tamadant nns. tmqqur bahra mk ttawsn iɣrbaɣn ɣ usbuɣlj n tiwangimin n inlmadn d twisi f ufham.

